            {
              "textEn": "<b>Lesson 2 • Talking about financial issues</b>"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "paragraphs": [
            {
              "textEn": "Juan and Diane work in the finance department of"
            },
            {
              "keyword": "delicious",
              "word": "Delicious"
            },
            {
              "textEn": "Delights, a company that makes snack foods. Here, they're discussing the financial projections for a new product line."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "paragraphs": [
            {
              "textEn": "<b>Juan:</b> I'm really excited about the launch of our new line of fat-free Delicious Delight donuts."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "paragraphs": [
            {
              "textEn": "<b>Diane:</b> Me too. But before we go any further, we'd better make sure this product line is going to be profitable."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "paragraphs": [
            {
              "textEn": "<b>Juan:</b> I did some"
            },
            {
              "keyword": "back-of-the-envelope calculations",
              "word": "back-of-the-envelope calculations"
            },
            {
              "textEn": ". Take a look."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "paragraphs": [
            {
              "textEn": "<b>Diane:</b> I see you've estimated $2 million for the new equipment. Where did you get that figure?"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "paragraphs": [
            {
              "textEn": "<b>Juan:</b> That's an "
            },
            {
              "keyword": "educated guess ",
              "word": "educated guess "
            },
            {
              "textEn": "based on some equipment I bought last year."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "paragraphs": [
            {
              "textEn": "<b>Diane:</b> You're going to need to double-check that. Using old estimates can get us"
            },
            {
              "keyword": "in hot water",
              "word": "in hot water"
            },
            {
              "textEn": "."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "paragraphs": [
            {
              "textEn": "<b>Juan:</b> No problem. I'll get on the phone with the manufacturer in Dallas and get a price quote."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "paragraphs": [
            {
              "textEn": "<b>Diane:</b> Do you have a sense for market demand? We should get the forecasts from the marketing department before we"
            },
            {
              "keyword": "crunch the numbers",
              "word": "crunch the numbers"
            },
            {
              "textEn": "."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "paragraphs": [
            {
              "textEn": "<b>Juan:</b> We don't have those yet. Mary from marketing said maybe we'd have them next week."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "paragraphs": [
            {
              "textEn": "<b>Diane:</b> It just"
            },
            {
              "keyword": "blow one's mind ",
              "word": "blows my mind "
            },
            {
              "textEn": "when marketing people want us to"
            },
            {
              "keyword": "run the numbers",
              "word": "run the numbers"
            },
            {
              "textEn": "and they don't bring us the information we need!"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "paragraphs": [
            {
              "textEn": "<b>Juan:</b> If we end up "
            },
            {
              "keyword": "in the red",
              "word": "in the red"
            },
            {
              "textEn": "on this project, it's going to be their"
            },
            {
              "keyword": "heads on the chopping block",
              "word": "heads on the chopping block"
            },
            {
              "textEn": ", not ours. They're the ones with P&L* responsibility!"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "paragraphs": [
            {
              "textEn": "<b>Diane:</b> Our CFO won't "
            },
            {
              "keyword": "give this project the green light",
              "word": "give this project the green light"
            },
            {
              "textEn": "until he sees all the numbers. If it doesn't look like we'll make money or at least"
            },
            {
              "keyword": "break even",
              "word": "break even"
            },
            {
              "textEn": ", he'll"
            },
            {
              "keyword": "pull the plug ",
              "word": "pull the plug ",
              "wordAudioSrc": "/dictionary/p/pull-the-plug.mp3"
            },
            {
              "textEn": "on the project."
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
