                },
                {
                  "id": "197e1327-a82b-469a-9210-47adc4a52d4e",
                  "label": "Yes, he told us that the project was a bad idea and that we should stop working on it.",
                  "isCorrect": false
                },
                {
                  "id": "715aa10b-2c9b-4124-a821-dec437ac0e02",
                  "label": "Yes, he's going to discuss the project with his wife and see what he thinks.",
                  "isCorrect": false
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "id": "177c2eb5-d2ae-4426-b976-a39434c08d57",
              "question": "2. Last year, our company made a loss on our new line of video games, but this year we'll make <b>break even</b>.",
