                  "label": "That would be great. My boss enjoys soaking in hot water.",
                  "isCorrect": false
                },
                {
                  "id": "6c130ddd-0089-4ff6-bfff-983c3931b4a8",
                  "label": "You're right. My boss always gets angry when he finds mistakes.",
                  "isCorrect": true
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "id": "1b9f8bd7-3ffc-42e6-88bd-5919d864ae5e",
              "question": "4. Our company is <b>in the red</b> again this quarter.",
              "options": [
                {
                  "id": "d2e3e21b-0626-49af-992b-55fefe924ef2",
                  "label": "Congratulations! When's the celebration party?",
                  "isCorrect": false
                },
                {
                  "id": "5354435d-56eb-433a-8d15-4cf1665dc4b8",
                  "label": "In the red again? I hope you don't go out of business!",
                  "isCorrect": true
                },
                {
                  "id": "33e0006d-e509-4780-8210-5674f4a1ea44",
                  "label": "In the red? That's okay. It's better than being in the black.",
                  "isCorrect": false
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "id": "eab9b289-57a0-46ac-a85f-a1faa09611dc",
              "question": "5. We should <b>pull the plug</b> on our online advertising campaign.",
              "options": [
                {
